# Get started

## Request access

All requests to access this API will be manually approved.

Email [support@integration-api.hmpps.service.justice.gov.uk](mailto:support@development.integration-api.hmpps.service.justice.gov.uk) to request access.

You may also request access to our non-live environment for testing purposes.
Include your public static IP address so that it can be added to our internal allow list.

You will receive login credentials including:

1. API Key
2. Client Certificate

For information on how to use these credentials, please see the [Authentication](/authentication.html) section.

## Explore available endpoints

You should now have access to all our [endpoints](../api/index.html).
